author: Gabriella Borter
title: U.S. doctors, nurses under strain as coronavirus rages on
description: U.S. doctors and nurses on the front lines of the coronavirus outbreak came under increasing stress on Friday as the number of cases skyrocketed and doctors and nurses were forced to ration care for an overwhelming number of patients.
content:
